These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-1::.
2 different games are played: whist, go
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: blues, house
1. the fan of blues is in an even position##4
2. the fan of house is the person playing go##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |
| Game   | go | whist |
| Music-Genre     | house    | blues   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-2::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: card-games, video-games
The people use 2 different means of transport: jet-ski, snowmobile
1. the person driving the jet-ski is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |
| Hobby   | video-games | card-games        |
| Transport      | jet-ski  | snowmobile |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-3::.
House: art-deco, victorian
There are 2 different favourite colors: pink, blood-red
1. the person who likes pink is in an odd position##4
2. the victorian house is on the left of the art-deco house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |
| House   | victorian    | art-deco |
| Color   | pink | blood-red |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-4::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  writer, social-worker
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: august, january
1. the social-worker is on the right of the writer##1
2. the person who's birthday is in january is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |
| Job   | writer      | social-worker |
| Birthday       | august | january    |

 #################################

 
