House: victorian, art-deco
1. the victorian house is the dannemann-smoker##1
2. the art-deco house is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |
| Cigar   | bolivar       | dannemann   |
| House   | art-deco | victorian |

